race.comment: REGAL PROBLEM (18) exciting filly who can go on with the job this campaign. Produced a good set of closing splits on resumption with a slashing third over 1400m at this track. Well drawn again with the claim and no excuses with her good turn of foot. PENSATIVA (10) good Highway mare ready to peak at her third run back. Proven at the trip and can get cover from the sticky barrier. Each way. HURRY MISS (15) jumped in grade in the heavy (8) going with a fading eighth over 1500m at this track in BM78 class. Was found to be (1/5) lame in the off-hind leg and will find this more to her liking. Minor place chance. LIKE LUKEY (9) is holding his form and gets a better set up for this. Stays in the mix.
